<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer10033274130438592468">Susannah Cahalan is the New York Times bestselling author of &quot;Brain on Fire: My Month of Madness,&quot; a memoir about her struggle with a rare autoimmune disease of the brain. She writes for the New York Post. Her work has also been featured in the New York Times, Scientific American Magazine, Glamour, Psychology Today, and others. </span>
  <span id="freeText10033274130438592468" style="display:none">Susannah Cahalan is the New York Times bestselling author of "Brain on Fire: My Month of Madness," a memoir about her struggle with a rare autoimmune disease of the brain. She writes for the New York Post. Her work has also been featured in the New York Times, Scientific American Magazine, Glamour, Psychology Today, and others. </span>
  <a data-text-id="10033274130438592468" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

